# Frontend conventions

- React 18 + Vite; pages in `frontend-react/src/pages/`
- API client: `frontend-react/src/services/api.js`
- Settings/context: `frontend-react/src/contexts/`
- Use existing Tailwind patterns in `index.css` and page components

## Build

```bash
cd frontend-react && npm run dev    # dev
npm run build:frontend              # from repo root
```

Match existing component structure; avoid new UI libraries without user approval.
